    • Constructor Detail

      • NativeIntArray

        public NativeIntArray(int size)
        Creates a new native array of size s, and keeps it wrapped in this object. Note that the elements of the array may not be initialised to 0. Use setAllTo(int) to initialise the array.
        Parameters:
        size - The size of the array to be created.
